                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-295-off1721 t18320405-295-cd1722"></join>, 3 breasts of mutton, value 2s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320405-295-victim2467" type="victimName">
