               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 30. - <rs id="t18320405-295-punish1726" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320405-295-punish1726" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-295-defend2465 t18320405-295-punish1726"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
